";'>: 2026. 07. 03.(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>금</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>) </span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>이내 예정</span></span></span><br/>\n<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>   ※ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>수강신청기간 </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>: 2026.</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>08</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>.03.(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>월</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>) ~ 08.</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>07.(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>금</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span><br/>\n<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>   ※ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>등록금 납부 기간 </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>: 2026. 08. 24.(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>월</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>) ~ 08. 28.(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>금</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span><br/>\n<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>   (</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>학사일정 상 변동될 수 있음</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>, </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>세부 내용은 추후 학사공지 참고</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span></p>\n<p><br/>\n<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>6. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>유의사항</span></span></span><br/>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>가</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>등록과 수강신청을 하지 않은 경우</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>, </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>재입학 허가 취소됨</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>(</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>무효 처리</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span><br/>\n  <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>나</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>재입학 당해 학기</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>(2026</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>학년도 </span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>2</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>학기</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>에 </span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>‘</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>일반휴학</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>’</span></span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>은 불허</span></span></span></u><br/>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>다</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>재입학 전의 기존 학적 및 상벌 사항 등은 재입학 이후에도 연속하여 적용됨</span></span><br/>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>라</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>성적경고누적으로 인한 제적생</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>(‘</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>재입학 후 성적경고 제적생</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>’ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>포함</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>)</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>은 제적일로부터 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>1</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>년 이상 </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>경과 후 재입학 가능</span></span><br/>\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>※ </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>재입학 후 성적경고 제적 </span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>성적경고누적으로 제적되어 재입학한 학생이 재입학 후</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>, </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>다시 성적경고를 </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>2</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>회 더 받은 경우</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>   마</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><u><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>학제개편으로 폐설된 학과 학생은 현재 운영 중인 관련 학과로 신청 가능</span></span></span></u></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>   바</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>. </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\"><span style='font-family: \"맑은 고딕\";'>단과대학 학사운영실의 추천이 있더라도 재입학 선발 기준에 따라 불합격 될 수 있음</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><sp